<title>USA: Maxim to issue 3.6 mln shrs at $16 each.</title>
<headline>Maxim to issue 3.6 mln shrs at $16 each.</headline>
<dateline>KENNESAW, Ga 1997-02-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Maxim Group Inc said Wednesday it was going to issue 3.6 million shares of its common stock at $16 each in a public offering.  </p>
<p>The company, which made a filing for the sale last month, said it was going to offer 3.17 million shares and shareholders the remaining 424,227.</p>
<p>It said it will use the proceeds from the offering to reduce amounts outstanding under its credit facilities.</p>
<p>Maxim operates and franchises retail floor-covering networks.</p>
<p>((-- New York Newsdesk 212 859-1610))</p>
